data.name: All NG Memories & All Beads
data.rules:
Beat the game with all of the following **Memories** or **Remnants**, as well as all 40 **Prayer Beads**:

- Gyoubu
- Lady Butterfly
- Genichiro
- Screen Monkeys
- Guardian Ape
- Headless Ape
- Corrupted Monk
- True Monk
- Great Shinobi
- Foster Father
- Divine Dragon
- Saint Isshin
- Hatred Demon

The order of collecting Memories/Beads does not matter, but a requirement is that an ending is achieved somewhere in the run.

##Timing

The timer starts automatically after starting New Game and stops directly after reaching the credits if Saint Isshin is the last Memory/Bead collected. If a player decides to collect another Memory/Bead other than Saint Isshin last, the player has to perform a quitout after they receive the final Memory/Bead and end the timer after quitting out.
